<h1>Mediation Statistics</h1>

<p>The <em><strong>Mediation statistics</strong></em> page provides the
following details.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Server Statistics</li>
  <li>Proxy Service Statistics</li>
  <li>Sequence Statistics</li>
  <li>Endpoint Statistics</li>
</ul>

<h2>Viewing Mediation Statistics</h2>
<ol>
  <li>In the navigator, under Monitor,
    click <strong>Mediation Statistics</strong>. The
    <em><strong>Mediation Statistics</strong></em> page appears.</li>
  <li>Click on a link to view the relevant statistics.
    Each link will take you to a new page that displays the component's
    mediation statistics.</li>
</ol>
